<p>Having a problem getting something to work or want to know why I setup something in a certain way? Ping me on Twitter <a href="http://twitter.com/hmfaysal">@hmfaysal</a> or <a href="https://github.com/hmfaysal/Jekyll-HMFAYSAL-V2-Theme/issues/new">file a GitHub Issue</a>. And if you make something cool with this theme feel free to let me know.</p>

